      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 I'm looking to find a new home for my trusty ride. It\u2019s been such a reliable companion and still runs like a total dream! It\u2019s in really great shape overall\u2014I've taken good care of it, though you'll find a few tiny signs of love from over the years. It's perfect for someone who wants a solid, comfy car without the brand-new price tag. Come take it for a spin, I know you'll love how it handles!",
