    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically robust E46 M3 featuring the iconic S54 3.2L inline-six engine and a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission. This example has undergone essential preventative maintenance, including a comprehensive VANOS system overhaul and structural subframe reinforcement to ensure chassis integrity under high-load cornering. The drivetrain is anchored by a factory limited-slip differential, providing exceptional traction and exit speed. Suspension kinematics are sharpened via Bilstein PSS10 coilovers, offering adjustable damping for varied road surfaces. While the exterior shows minor patina consistent with a well-loved driver\u2019s car, the internal mechanical tolerances and throttle response remain sharp, offering a visceral, analog experience for the discerning enthusiast.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
